Phakathi kwamathimba aseZimbabwe kubalwa awe-African Union neSouthern African Development Community (SADC) aveze ukuthi ayakwamukela ukunqoba kukaMengameli Emmerson Mnangagwa. Selokhu kuphume imiphumela yokhetho umholi weMovement for Democratic Change (MDC) Alliance, uMnuz Nelson Chamisa, uthe akahambisani nayo waze waya enkantolo. UMnuz Moussa Faki Mahamat, onguSihlalo we-AU Commission, uthe bazoqhubeka nokuhlala eZimbabwe ukuze baqinisekise ukuthi intando yabantu iyaqhubeka. Khonamanjalo, izolo abadayisi basemgwaqweni bakhale ngoMnangagwa emuva kokususwa kwabo ezitaladini zaseHarare. Laba badayisi bathi uMnangagwa ubasusile emigwaqweni yaseHarare ngoba bevotele amaqembu aphikisayo okhethweni lwangesonto eledlule. Izolo abadayisi baku-4th Street eHarare bebematasa bekhipha impahla ezindaweni abadayisela kuzona begadwe ngamaphoyisa namasosha. Bekungokokuqala ngqa abavoti eHarare bevotela amaqembu aphikisayo ngobuningi babo njengoba kuthiwa amavoti amaningi aye kumholi weMDC-Alliance. UMnuz Stan Zvorwadza, ohola abadayisi basemgwaqweni eHarare, uthe usola ukuthi ukungasekwa kukaMnangagwa eHarare yikona okwenza baxoshwe. Abanye abadayisi abacele ukungadalulwa batshele i-ANA ukuthi bakhathazekile ngoba sekunomengameli ojezisa abavotele amaqembu aphikisayo. “Umholi akufanele akhombise ukuba nenhliziyo embi uma engavotelwanga endaweni ethile. Kufanele aqinisekise ukuthi isizwe siyabumbana alandele umthetho wezwe,” kusho uMnuz Petros Ngaabe oyisitshudeni esibuye sidayise emgwaqweni. UDkt Pedzisai Ruhanya uthe kubuhlungu ukususwa kwabadayisi basemgwaqweni ekubeni uMengameli Mnangagwa wayethembise ukuthi uzothuthukisa impilo yabo. Abanye abadayisi bathe ngesikhathi sikaMugabe abakaze basuswe emgwaqweni ngoba ngesikhathi iMDC izama ukubasusa iZanuPF kaMugabe yayibavikela. UMnangagwa uthole u-50.8% wamavoti okhethweni lwangesonto elidlule kwathi uChamisa wathola u-44.3% wamavoti. Abantu baphinde bakhala ngokuhlaselwa ngamasosha abashaye ngezimvubu, bathe bayasaba ukushuthwa ngoba abavela emaphephandabeni bayahlukunyezwa. IMDC-Alliance ithumele isitatimende lapho iveze ukuthi kujutshwe amasosha angu-2 500 eHarare, Epworth, Chitungwiza, Glen View naseDzivarasekwa lapho abantu betalajwa ngemvubu nsukuzonke. “Amasosha ahlukumeza abantu abavotele iMDC-Alliance futhi ajutshwe ezindaweni ukuze asabise abantu,” kusho iMDC-Alliance. IZimbabwe Defence Force ithe ayikaze ijube amasosha ahlukumeza abantu isho nokuthi abantu kufanele babikele amaphoyisa uma kukhona abazibiza ngamasosha ababatalabhayo.